{"tid":2115424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"當元朗係condom? 自稱抗爭派班人去咗邊？","createTime":"2020-07-19T13:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T15:47:57.000Z","uid":204214,"like":14,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"89b4673e4eea16b0f0629483099e16398807481f","tid":2115424,"uid":204214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T13:19:21.000Z","msg":"今日見到天水連線話自己個遊行取消<br />\n由區議員同抗爭派啲代行<br />\n點知現場得個小貓三四隻<br />\n我仲以為本土抗爭派已成主流添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日有幾多抗爭派嚟咗大家心照<br />\n又話遊行 遊咗去邊？<br />\n打個卡就話自己嚟咗幫咗手？<br />\n最後又係得返天水連線個四個on9仔遊行<br />\n仲要比人拉埋<br />\n<br />\n你班抗爭派一句都冇交帶就走撚曬<br />\n幾次同記者交帶都係林進同伍健偉<br />\n我真係好懷疑香港係咪淨係得佢地會行到咁前<br />\n仲話咩同手足一齊並肩作戰乜乜柒柒<br />\n自己友都拋棄 <br />\n你哋班自稱抗爭派嘅撚樣好打極都有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b7672b144890a5d49821d789cd7db17fb3d55d","tid":2115424,"uid":99654,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T13:24:26.000Z","msg":"依家天水連線4個區議員仲比人拉左係狗屋，其他人影都冇隻，我都想問下佢地點解唔幫下手，希望佢地4個冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ea097cde3029a4b4175265bd6f54e962f62fd0","tid":2115424,"uid":305137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T13:28:25.000Z","msg":"天水連線唔係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9f17dff99c2e1560651df99fe6d85fa6b60071","tid":2115424,"uid":204214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d9b7672b144890a5d49821d789cd7db17fb3d55d","tid":2115424,"uid":99654,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T13:24:26.000Z","msg":"依家天水連線4個區議員仲比人拉左係狗屋，其他人影都冇隻，我都想問下佢地點解唔幫下手，希望佢地4個冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 